metadata.title: Journee Collection Womens Sarah Bootie with Soft Square Toe and Contrasting Heel Fabric
features: SARAH BOOTIE: Trendy, unique, and bold all combine to create the Sarah bootie by Journee Collection. This stand out bootie features gorgeous designer details featuring a different heel pattern on each of the four colors. The toe shape is a soft square design, going up the shaft where this boot sits perfectly just above the ankle.
MEDIUM WIDTH FOOTBEDS: These shoes are available in a medium shoe width. All measurements are approximate and were taken using a size 6. Please note measurements may vary slightly by size.

BLOCKED HEEL: The 3" block heel is the perfect size to give you a touch of height without making it difficult to walk. Whether you’re going out with your girlfriends for a night on the town, heading to work, or running errands, you’ll love the comfortable, lightweight feel that our fancy shoes provide. They go great with casual jeans and a cute tee or something a little more formal, like a sexy dress, a romper, or another fashionable outfit.

HIGH-QUALITY BOOTS: Every women’s shoe in our collection of boots at Journee Collection is created with the finest materials available. With sturdy construction and padded footbeds, you can be sure that our classy boots won’t fall apart like many shoes on the market.

JOURNEE COLLECTION SHOES: At Journee Collection, we believe that wearing the right shoes can change your entire day. Wearing eye-catching shoes can make any woman feel confident and empowered. And who doesn’t want to feel that way? We make every pair of shoes with you in mind. Go for an elegant riding boot or a fun-printed rubber boot — we have them all in our wide collection. You will feel the difference.
description: Dish out some style hot off the runway wearing the Journee Collection(r) Sarah Bootie featuring a faux leather, pull-on with exposed side zip closure, almond-toe silhouette, and two-tone design. Fabric lining. Lightly padded insole. Covered block heel.
